<div class="space-y-0">

  <%# Step 1: 프롬프트 복사 (interactive — blue accent) %>
  <div data-step="1" class="relative flex gap-4 pb-6">
    <%# Vertical connector line (hidden for last step) %>
    <div class="absolute left-5 top-10 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <%# Numbered circle %>
    <div data-step-number="1"
         aria-hidden="true"
         class="relative z-10 flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-sm font-bold text-white ring-4 ring-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-500 dark:ring-blue-900/40">
      1
    </div>

    <%# Card body %>
    <div class="flex-1 min-w-0 rounded-lg border border-blue-200 bg-blue-50 p-4 dark:border-blue-800 dark:bg-blue-950/30">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-200 mb-1">프롬프트 복사</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-3">이 도구에서 AI 분석 프롬프트를 클립보드에 복사하세요</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 mb-3">
        아래 버튼을 눌러 AI 분석용 프롬프트를 클립보드에 복사하세요.
      </p>
      <% if step1_action? %>
        <%= step1_action %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# Step 2: AI 채팅에 붙여넣기 (explanatory — slate accent) %>
  <div data-step="2" class="relative flex gap-4 pb-6">
    <div class="absolute left-5 top-10 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div data-step-number="2"
         aria-hidden="true"
         class="relative z-10 flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-slate-400 text-sm font-bold text-white dark:bg-slate-600">
      2
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 min-w-0 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-800/60">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 mb-1">AI에 붙여넣기</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-3">ChatGPT · Claude · Gemini 등 AI 채팅에 PDF와 프롬프트를 함께 올리세요</p>

      <%# Inline SVG: chat window with PDF attachment and pasted prompt %>
      <div class="mb-3 flex justify-center">
        <svg aria-hidden="true" width="200" height="130" viewBox="0 0 200 130" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
             class="rounded-md border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600">
          <%# Chat window background %>
          <rect width="200" height="130" rx="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-white dark:text-slate-900" opacity="0.6"/>
          <%# Top bar %>
          <rect width="200" height="22" rx="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700"/>
          <rect y="16" width="200" height="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700"/>
          <circle cx="12" cy="11" r="3.5" fill="currentColor" class="text-red-400"/>
          <circle cx="22" cy="11" r="3.5" fill="currentColor" class="text-yellow-400"/>
          <circle cx="32" cy="11" r="3.5" fill="currentColor" class="text-green-400"/>
          <text x="90" y="15" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">ChatGPT / Claude / Gemini</text>
          <%# PDF attachment chip %>
          <rect x="10" y="28" width="54" height="20" rx="4" fill="currentColor" class="text-blue-100 dark:text-blue-900/60"/>
          <text x="18" y="41" font-size="7" fill="currentColor" class="text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300">📄 경매.pdf</text>
          <%# Prompt text bubble (user message) %>
          <rect x="10" y="54" width="145" height="42" rx="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-600" opacity="0.15"/>
          <text x="17" y="66" font-size="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">다음 법원경매 물건을 분석해</text>
          <text x="17" y="75" font-size="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">주세요. 아래 형식으로 답해</text>
          <text x="17" y="84" font-size="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">주세요: { "result": ... }</text>
          <%# Paste cursor hint %>
          <rect x="155" y="54" width="2" height="12" rx="1" fill="currentColor" class="text-blue-500"/>
          <%# Bottom input bar %>
          <rect x="10" y="108" width="168" height="16" rx="4" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-100 dark:text-slate-700"/>
          <text x="18" y="119" font-size="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-400">메시지 입력...</text>
          <rect x="178" y="108" width="16" height="16" rx="4" fill="currentColor" class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-600"/>
          <text x="186" y="119" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" fill="white">↑</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        복사한 프롬프트와 법원경매 PDF 파일을 AI 채팅창에 함께 올려서 분석을 요청하세요.
        AI가 분석을 마치면 긴 텍스트로 결과를 답해 줍니다.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# Step 3: AI 답변 JSON 복사 (explanatory — slate accent) %>
  <div data-step="3" class="relative flex gap-4 pb-6">
    <div class="absolute left-5 top-10 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div data-step-number="3"
         aria-hidden="true"
         class="relative z-10 flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-slate-400 text-sm font-bold text-white dark:bg-slate-600">
      3
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 min-w-0 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-800/60">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 mb-1">JSON 답변 복사</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-3">AI가 답한 텍스트 전체를 그대로 복사하세요</p>

      <%# Inline SVG: chat response with JSON text selected %>
      <div class="mb-3 flex justify-center">
        <svg aria-hidden="true" width="200" height="130" viewBox="0 0 200 130" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
             class="rounded-md border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600">
          <%# Background %>
          <rect width="200" height="130" rx="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-white dark:text-slate-900" opacity="0.6"/>
          <%# Top bar %>
          <rect width="200" height="22" rx="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700"/>
          <rect y="16" width="200" height="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-200 dark:text-slate-700"/>
          <circle cx="12" cy="11" r="3.5" fill="currentColor" class="text-red-400"/>
          <circle cx="22" cy="11" r="3.5" fill="currentColor" class="text-yellow-400"/>
          <circle cx="32" cy="11" r="3.5" fill="currentColor" class="text-green-400"/>
          <text x="90" y="15" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">AI 답변</text>
          <%# AI response bubble (assistant) — left aligned %>
          <rect x="10" y="28" width="160" height="70" rx="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-100 dark:text-slate-800"/>
          <%# Highlighted / selected JSON text %>
          <rect x="14" y="32" width="100" height="9" rx="2" fill="currentColor" class="text-blue-200 dark:text-blue-800" opacity="0.8"/>
          <text x="16" y="40" font-size="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200" font-family="monospace">{ "result": "낙찰가 추정",</text>
          <rect x="14" y="43" width="130" height="9" rx="2" fill="currentColor" class="text-blue-200 dark:text-blue-800" opacity="0.8"/>
          <text x="16" y="51" font-size="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200" font-family="monospace">  "bid_price": 240000000,</text>
          <rect x="14" y="54" width="115" height="9" rx="2" fill="currentColor" class="text-blue-200 dark:text-blue-800" opacity="0.8"/>
          <text x="16" y="62" font-size="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200" font-family="monospace">  "risk_grade": "B",</text>
          <rect x="14" y="65" width="80" height="9" rx="2" fill="currentColor" class="text-blue-200 dark:text-blue-800" opacity="0.8"/>
          <text x="16" y="73" font-size="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200" font-family="monospace">  "summary": "..." }</text>
          <text x="16" y="90" font-size="6" fill="currentColor" class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">전체 텍스트를 선택 → 복사</text>
          <%# Copy hint arrow %>
          <path d="M 158 50 L 175 50 L 175 70 L 165 70" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-dasharray="3 2" fill="none" class="text-blue-500"/>
          <%# Copy icon %>
          <rect x="170" y="40" width="18" height="18" rx="3" fill="currentColor" class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-600" opacity="0.9"/>
          <text x="179" y="52" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" fill="white">⎘</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        AI가 답해 준 내용에는 <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">JSON</strong>이 들어 있습니다.
        <strong class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">JSON은 AI가 답해 주는 글자 모양의 데이터입니다.</strong>
        모양은 어렵지만 그대로 복사해서 다음 단계에 붙이기만 하면 됩니다.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# Step 4: 결과 업로드 (interactive — blue accent, no connector line below) %>
  <div data-step="4" class="relative flex gap-4">
    <div data-step-number="4"
         aria-hidden="true"
         class="relative z-10 flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-sm font-bold text-white ring-4 ring-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-500 dark:ring-blue-900/40">
      4
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 min-w-0 rounded-lg border border-blue-200 bg-blue-50 p-4 dark:border-blue-800 dark:bg-blue-950/30">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-200 mb-1">결과 업로드</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-3">이 도구에 복사한 결과를 붙여넣거나 파일로 올리세요</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 mb-3">
        AI로부터 받은 JSON 결과를 파일로 업로드하거나 직접 붙여넣으세요.
      </p>
      <% if step4_action? %>
        <%= step4_action %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
